This project is tittled Nthiga Denis project and is  a small application that allow a user
to add books into a list

The applications allows a user to mannually write books add books into a list by physically typing the book tittle and  the book author

it also has a link that allows the user to see the list of book he/she has typed in

the application also has an about me section that allows the user to  access the information about the creator of the app

The application also incorporates a function that allows user to delete a single entity of book in the list through a delete button

The applicaion is pure Javascript with no farameworks used is made up of 
1.    3 javascript files
2.     1 css file for styling the webpage
3.     1 HTML file 


The application also includes a fetch funtions that allows user to POST data  to the local API